race.description: Paul Taggett Kitchens Country Boosted Hcp (C3)
race.comment: CONFEDERATE LADY (9) progressive mare deep into her prep who looks ready to run a strong 1110m. Chased hard from just off the pace with a fighting second over 1005m at Ballina. Kept fresh and can tag the good tempo. Top-three prospect. KIRRA'S SISTER (8) bounced off her good first-up second, with a slick on-pace victory over 1100m at Grafton. Capable of repeating the effort in this harder contest. CONSIDERED (7) talented mare resuming. Has impressed in her two slick trial wins and looks primed for a first-up victory. KEVIN MCKEEN (6) rewarded for his consistency when a tough on-pace winner over 1258m at Taree. Can go on with it now from the inside gate.
